## 12. F-Q-6-B/C 양자 Hamiltonian build + VQE (v7 land 2026-05-11)

방법: `_qiskit_bridge/module/pocket_active_space.py` + `tests/quantum_{h2o,drug}_vqe_v7.py`. qiskit 2.4.1 + qiskit-nature 0.7.2 + qiskit-algorithms 0.4.0 + pyscf 2.13.0 + rdkit 2026.3.1. Active space = 2e/2o 또는 4e/4o (HOMO/LUMO frontier, NOT pocket-restricted). VQE = EfficientSU2 depth=1 + COBYLA 400 iters + COBYLA tol 1e-8 + seed 7 random initial point + StatevectorEstimator V2.

honest scope: 본 §12 = **build pipeline validation + frontier-orbital VQE** 까지. 실제 drug-target binding 평가는 pocket-restricted active space (F-Q-6-D ramp, catalytic residue orbital indices 명시) 필수 — 본 §12 산출 energy 는 frontier 2e/2o 의 isolated 분자 ground state delta, **binding 와 무관**.

### 12.1. H2O baseline (F-Q-6-B1/B2 — Phase β closure)

#### 12.1.a. EfficientSU2 depth=1 (initial path)

| label | nelecas/ncas | n_qubits | n_pauli | CASCI E (Ha)     | VQE E (Ha)        | delta (mHa) | delta (µHa) | chem-acc | sub-µHa | iter |
|-------|--------------|----------|---------|-------------------|--------------------|-------------|-------------|----------|---------|------|
| `F-Q-6-B1` | 2e/2o    | 2        | 5       | -74.96417684     | -74.96412104       | 0.0558      | 55.8        | ✅ PASS   | ❌      | 400  |
| `F-Q-6-B2` | 4e/4o    | 6        | 24      | -74.97034075     | -74.96198066       | 8.3601      | 8360.1      | ❌ FAIL   | ❌      | 400  |

#### 12.1.b. UCCSD reps=1 (F-Q-6-B2 closure ramp — v7 Phase β)

EfficientSU2 depth=1 의 B2 8.36 mHa fail → qiskit-nature UCCSD ansatz (HF initial state + reps=1, 26-param 6-qubit) + ParityMapper 동일 active space 재시도. 3 optimizer 비교:

| optimizer | maxiter | iter actual | params | VQE E (Ha)       | delta (mHa) | delta (µHa) | chem-acc | sub-µHa | wall (s) |
|-----------|---------|--------------|--------|-------------------|-------------|-------------|----------|---------|----------|
| COBYLA    | 600     | 600          | 26     | -74.97034045     | 0.000295    | **0.30** ⭐ | ✅ PASS   | ✅ PASS  | 159.3    |
| SLSQP     | 300     | 273          | 26     | -74.97034040     | 0.000341    | 0.34        | ✅ PASS   | ✅ PASS  | 62.9     |
| L_BFGS_B  | 200     | 351          | 26     | -74.97034045     | 0.000295    | 0.30        | ✅ PASS   | ✅ PASS  | 75.1     |

핵심:
- ⭐ **F-Q-6-B2 CLOSED** — UCCSD reps=1 + 임의 optimizer 모두 sub-µHa 도달 (0.29-0.34 µHa).
- ⭐ **4-order-of-magnitude 개선** — EfficientSU2 depth=1 8360 µHa → UCCSD 0.30 µHa.
- SLSQP 최적 비용 (273 iter, 63s) — COBYLA/L_BFGS_B 와 동일 정확도지만 wall 2.5x 빠름.
- ramp 함의: 6+ qubit Hamiltonian 에서 EfficientSU2 depth=1 한계 명확 → UCCSD 가 표준 ansatz 로 굳어짐.

